  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Attribute: NHS CONTINUING HEALTHCARE COMMISSIONED SERVICES INDICATOR - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>

  <p>
An indication of whether the 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">Clinical Commissioning Group</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_clinical_commissioning_group">CCG</xref>
) authorises another 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_organisation">ORGANISATION</xref>
 to exercise any of its 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_nhs_continuing_healthcare">NHS Continuing Healthcare</xref>
 functions on its behalf, for example, 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_commissioning_support_unit">Commissioning Support Unit</xref>
 (
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_commissioning_support_unit">CSU</xref>
), 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_nhs_trust">NHS Trust</xref>
, section 75 arrangement with 
    <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
            keyref="business_definition_local_authority">Local Authority</xref>
.  </p>
